(h) The accrediting agency provides for the public correction of incorrect or misleading information about_
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(1) The accreditation status of an accredited or preaccredited institution or program; 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(2) The contents of reports of site team visitors; and 
