(i) Any funds appropriated to carry out this program; 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(ii) Its allotment of any funds appropriated under the SSIG Program; and 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(iii) Any funds appropriated to carry out the NEISP Program; and 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(2) The Secretary_ 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(i) Does not designate as eligible for participation in a Title IV, HEA program any institution seeking initial participation
in that program, any branch campus for which an institution seeks an initial designation of eligibility under 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
34 CFR part 600, or any institution that has undergone a change in ownership that results in a change in control as determined
in 34 CFR part 600, that is located in that State; 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(ii) Grants only provisional certification, as determined in 34 CFR part 668, to an institution in that State not described
in paragraph (e)(2)(i) of this section; and 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(iii) May_
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(A) Establish the review standards for that State described in &sect;667.21; and 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(B) Carry out, or arrange to carry out, the State's other responsibilities and requirements under this part.
