&sect;667.5
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=89 g=1 f=1 -->
Criteria the Secretary uses to refer institutions to a SPRE for review. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

