&sect;667.6 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=89 g=1 f=1 -->
SPRE selection of institutions for review. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
A SPRE may review an institution under this part that was not referred by the Secretary if_
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(a) The SPRE_ 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(1)(i) Determines that the institution meets a referral criterion in &sect;667.5 based on more recent data available
to the SPRE; or 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(ii) Has reason to believe the institution is engaged in fraudulent practices; and 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(2) Requests the Secretary to approve its review of that institution; and 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(b) The Secretary_
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(1) Approves that request; or 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(2) Does not respond to the SPRE's request within 21 days after the date the Secretary receives that request. 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

