<!-- PJG ITAG l=80 g=1 f=1 -->
&sect;667.7 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=89 g=1 f=1 -->
Notice to SPRE of Federal actions. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
(a) If the Secretary takes an action against an institution, the Secretary notifies the SPRE of the State in which the
institution is located within 10 days of taking that action. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(b) If the Secretary is informed that another Federal agency is taking an action against an institution, the Secretary
notifies the SPRE of the State in which the institution is located as soon as possible but not later than 10 days after
learning of that action. 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG QTAG 04 -->
<!-- PJG /QTAG -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

