<!-- PJG ITAG l=80 g=1 f=1 -->
&sect;667.8 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=89 g=1 f=1 -->
Institutions with locations in more than one State. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
(a) If an institution that is subject to a referral has locations in more than one State, the Secretary refers the institution
to the SPRE in each State in which the institution is located and informs each SPRE of the other States in which the institution
is located. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(b) The SPRE of the State in which the main campus of the institution is located has the principal responsibility for
reviewing that institution. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(c) If a branch campus or additional location of an institution is in a State other than the State in which the institution's
main campus is located, the SPRE of the State in which that branch campus or additional location is located_
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(1) May review that branch campus or additional location before a SPRE review is conducted of the main campus of that
institution; 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(2) May delay its review of that branch campus or additional location until a SPRE review is conducted of the main campus
of that institution; or 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(3) May choose not to review that branch campus or additional location if_
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(i) The SPRE of the State in which the main campus of that institution is located reviews that institution and makes
no significant findings; and 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(ii) The State's allotment is insufficient to allow the SPRE to review all referred institutions. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(d) An institution, its branch campuses, and additional locations are subject to the review standards of the State
in which they are located. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(e) Notwithstanding paragraphs (b) and (c) of this section, to review a referred institution that has locations in
more than one State, the SPREs of those States may enter into an agreement under which the SPREs may alter the review
responsibilities set forth in paragraphs (b) and (c) of this section. 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG QTAG 04 -->
<!-- PJG /QTAG -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

